Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.69,0:02:03.01,Default,actress,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.99,0:02:07.54,Default,actor,0000,0000,0000,,Because I wanted to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.69,0:02:15.71,Default,actress,0000,0000,0000,,But you went far away beyond my reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.47,0:02:19.30,Default,actor,0000,0000,0000,,But I wanted to see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.39,0:02:23.79,Default,actor,0000,0000,0000,,Love is beyond time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.37,0:02:43.96,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Aren't movies nice? There's always a happy ending.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.36,0:02:56.20,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Love is beyond time, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.44,0:03:01.50,Default,actress,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.25,0:03:05.25,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.00,0:03:08.09,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.34,0:03:10.96,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you liked the movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.03,0:03:11.71,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.37,0:03:13.03,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.51,0:03:14.32,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Tomomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.70,0:03:17.32,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,If you love him, you can see him, beyond time and distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.49,0:03:20.72,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you can be like that with senpai someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.73,0:03:25.55,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, the reality isn't all that convenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.91,0:03:28.25,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you be honest to yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.78,0:03:31.52,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Tomomi! That's my ice cream!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.79,0:03:40.30,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Are you OK, Mikage?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.38,0:03:42.50,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.61,0:03:44.53,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry, lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.30,0:03:55.27,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,It's a scratch, but make sure to disinfect the injury when you get home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.14,0:03:57.30,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.61,0:04:01.72,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing at all. It was my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.22,0:04:04.69,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,So, please don't get mad at the scarf.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.99,0:04:06.41,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.02,0:04:11.89,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, because it landed on you, I didn't lose it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.78,0:04:14.94,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,I have to thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.55,0:04:17.14,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Is it important to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.02,0:04:26.01,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,I'll return it to you later, so can I have your address?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.14,0:04:29.66,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,It's quite all right. I really have to thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.32,0:04:31.43,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Please?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.87,0:04:35.53,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,If you insist. Then can we meet here again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.88,0:04:36.51,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.89,0:04:41.49,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I'll be here for the next several days.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.72,0:04:44.99,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,When you feel like returning it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.03,0:04:52.23,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,That old lady was a bit strange, wasn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.05,0:04:55.38,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,At least she could've told us her address.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.21,0:04:59.52,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,The scarf that landed on you seemed very important to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.54,0:05:04.01,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Looked pretty old. You could say it was an antique.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.23,0:05:07.42,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,That's for one, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.98,0:05:08.58,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.46,0:05:13.18,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,There might be something else to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.99,0:05:18.17,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Something else? You're thinking too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.52,0:05:19.50,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,But you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.08,0:05:23.87,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,You wouldn't keep old things unless they're very important to you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.07,0:05:26.99,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Listen. It's not a movie, get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.63,0:05:30.39,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,But you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.78,0:05:34.03,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Kurashige-senpai and you could work things out far better than the movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.05,0:05:35.23,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,That's what Noda-kun said...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.15,0:05:41.68,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,What is Oink Noda's idea to go to the movie?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.76,0:05:46.59,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you like it?... Good night!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.69,0:05:48.07,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Tomomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.27,0:05:50.70,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.93,0:05:55.90,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Noda!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.48,0:05:58.56,Default,Noda,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Mikage.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.72,0:06:04.17,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get this straight. I don't need that stupid movie to comfort myself, get it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.64,0:06:06.62,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.23,0:06:08.31,Default,Noda,0000,0000,0000,,So she figured it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.19,0:06:16.29,Default,Noda,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit, you're the one who wanted to cheer her up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.68,0:06:17.68,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.87,0:06:21.76,Default,Yamagishi,0000,0000,0000,,Noda, she's gonna get tough on you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.21,0:06:24.66,Default,Noda,0000,0000,0000,,Darn. Can't stand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.13,0:06:47.37,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mikage, are you still mad at me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.13,0:06:49.15,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Not really.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.98,0:06:55.28,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I asked Noda-kun for an idea, so don't get mad at him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.54,0:07:00.79,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Got it. Anyway, I'll go by the park tomorrow after school.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.54,0:07:03.07,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come with me, will you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.42,0:07:24.17,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.82,0:07:30.14,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry you had to come all the way out to here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.51,0:07:35.13,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for putting up with an elderly's whim.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.88,0:07:40.24,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,You reminded me of the old days.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.61,0:07:41.29,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.57,0:07:47.64,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. I once ran around at this spot and scratched my knee.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.00,0:07:51.48,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,The scarf is quite old, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.63,0:07:59.17,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. You could say, it was a memory of my first love.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.46,0:08:03.79,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't mind, I'd like to hear about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.23,0:08:05.72,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.81,0:08:06.44,Default,Tomo&Mika,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.32,0:08:15.61,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,It was so long ago. Back when I was about your age...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.84,0:08:34.17,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,Back then, dance parties were held aboard that ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.58,0:08:37.67,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,I begged my parents to be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.54,0:08:48.54,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,It was such a beautiful sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.93,0:08:53.50,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,I was quite desperate to act mature.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.93,0:09:03.88,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,My brand new dress was ruined, and my knee was scratched.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.88,0:09:08.06,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,I was just about ready to cry. Just then...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.54,0:09:12.84,Default,man,0000,0000,0000,,Are you OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.43,0:09:17.46,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,A young man helped me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.20,0:09:23.38,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,And he put his scarf on my knee without any hesitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.90,0:10:39.59,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,And what happened between you and him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.81,0:10:44.26,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,That was all. I never knew his name, and it was over.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.47,0:10:46.12,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.29,0:10:47.26,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.72,0:10:48.76,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.60,0:10:55.60,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,It was a time when you really couldn't fall in love as freely as it is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.36,0:11:01.44,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,And I had to leave the country with my parents soon afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.98,0:11:03.58,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Then, nothing since then?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.05,0:11:07.70,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, but now that I'm visiting Japan,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.70,0:11:11.09,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,somehow I ended up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.90,0:11:22.36,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,I was dreaming that if I have the scarf on, I may find the man again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.09,0:11:49.85,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Say Mikage. Why don't we find him?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.39,0:11:51.01,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Find who?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.80,0:11:53.42,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The old lady's first love.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.64,0:11:56.14,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Without knowing his name?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.33,0:12:01.99,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He could be thinking about her too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.41,0:12:05.86,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No way. It was so long ago, wasn't it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.19,0:12:13.20,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Let's try to find him. We'll never know till we try.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.93,0:12:16.92,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,I'll think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.98,0:12:24.61,Default,elder,0000,0000,0000,,What about the ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.31,0:12:29.27,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember about the time when they used to have parties on that ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.14,0:12:33.00,Default,elder,0000,0000,0000,,What about Pachinko?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.01,0:12:34.98,Default,Yamagishi,0000,0000,0000,,Not Pachinko. Party!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.18,0:12:38.51,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure we can find out something from her?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.98,0:12:41.74,Default,Yamagishi,0000,0000,0000,,She's the oldest person around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.16,0:12:43.73,Default,elder,0000,0000,0000,,What about folklore?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.89,0:12:46.51,Default,librarian,0000,0000,0000,,Parties aboard the ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.76,0:12:50.10,Default,Noda,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. We need the list of guests for our social study research.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.17,0:12:54.73,Default,Yamagishi,0000,0000,0000,,Do we have to go through all these lists?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.15,0:12:57.53,Default,Yamagishi,0000,0000,0000,,There were lots of parties aboard the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.77,0:13:01.00,Default,Yamagishi,0000,0000,0000,,It could take years to look through them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.00,0:13:02.08,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Guess it's no go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.30,0:13:05.22,Default,Noda,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you ask her for more details?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.50,0:13:06.27,Default,Yamagishi,0000,0000,0000,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.57,0:13:09.01,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,But we can't let her raise hope for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.39,0:13:11.59,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Think of the shock if we can't find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.29,0:13:14.26,Default,Noda,0000,0000,0000,,But you know? ...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.65,0:13:18.87,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,So love didn't go beyond time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.28,0:13:27.44,Default,Yamagishi,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot. I didn't bring an umbrella.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.20,0:13:34.00,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,No way she'd be here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.51,0:13:56.28,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,We can't do anything for her even if we're ESPers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.34,0:13:59.96,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,So, things don't work out that easily after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.79,0:14:06.44,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Reality doesn't work like fairy tales.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.96,0:14:07.61,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.99,0:14:10.19,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.40,0:14:14.02,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,It could be trying to tell us something.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.37,0:14:16.12,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,About the old lady's first love?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.55,0:14:18.95,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Don't know. But we might find out something.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.59,0:14:39.94,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.62,0:14:41.81,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like a hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.21,0:14:46.46,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.48,0:14:54.24,Default,son,0000,0000,0000,,Father, you sure surprised me. All of a sudden you insisted on coming to Yokohama.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.93,0:14:58.74,Default,man,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I just remembered something.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.49,0:15:02.33,Default,son,0000,0000,0000,,As long as we make it on time to the meeting in Osaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.60,0:15:06.03,Default,son,0000,0000,0000,,That reminds me, you lived in the area when you were young, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.67,0:15:11.09,Default,man,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. There used to be parties aboard that ship frequently.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.66,0:15:16.00,Default,son,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you chuckling?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.77,0:15:18.73,Default,son,0000,0000,0000,,Remembering about your first love?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.45,0:15:25.05,Default,man,0000,0000,0000,,What a corny thing I did. I met such a jumpy girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.78,0:15:29.07,Default,man,0000,0000,0000,,I put a scarf on her scratched knee.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.75,0:15:32.87,Default,son,0000,0000,0000,,So there were days like that for you too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.28,0:15:36.18,Default,man,0000,0000,0000,,You could say it was first love.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.06,0:15:40.53,Default,son,0000,0000,0000,,We should go for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.02,0:15:50.64,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go see her. She may want to see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.16,0:15:58.83,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.08,0:16:02.39,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Old lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.56,0:16:06.05,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Old lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.97,0:16:10.65,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Old lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.69,0:16:31.72,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you wanna go? We only got a five minute break.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.18,0:16:34.51,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,We're just going to tell her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.87,0:16:36.30,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Can't we wait till after school?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.20,0:16:41.75,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,You're a good girl, Mikage.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.99,0:16:55.01,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,She isn't here after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.83,0:16:58.34,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do? We might not see her again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.42,0:17:01.81,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage, the break is almost over.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.28,0:17:19.36,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Old lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.00,0:17:21.83,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.21,0:17:23.57,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,We found him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.38,0:17:26.82,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,We found your first love.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.11,0:17:29.71,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,And he remembers about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.28,0:17:31.60,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,We might still have time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.99,0:17:34.00,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Will you come with us? Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.62,0:17:35.47,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.18,0:17:39.69,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,That's good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.67,0:17:53.41,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Didn't you say you want to see him again?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.90,0:17:56.80,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, I thought so for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.63,0:18:03.18,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,But looking at the ship, I decided that a memory is a memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.30,0:18:03.89,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.53,0:18:08.85,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,The ship grows old too, doesn't it? Just like I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.49,0:18:15.40,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,What's in my memory is when everything was pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.61,0:18:21.27,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,And I was also young and energetic just as you two are now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.28,0:18:27.26,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,He's also an old person like I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.10,0:18:31.14,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,We are just reflecting back on old days.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.23,0:18:36.73,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,So, I want him to remember me as I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.44,0:18:39.06,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.13,0:18:43.78,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he feels the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.37,0:18:52.50,Default,son,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, father?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.04,0:18:57.16,Default,man,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I should've went to see the ship before I left.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.68,0:18:59.24,Default,man,0000,0000,0000,,It's OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.94,0:19:07.02,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.39,0:19:13.12,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,I have family back at home. So, I'm here to say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.99,0:19:18.66,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,This is for remembering meeting you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.66,0:19:21.02,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,But isn't this your important... We can't take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.88,0:19:29.00,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,Then will you give it back to the owner of the scarf? How is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.01,0:19:34.65,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to the ship, now I have two memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.71,0:19:39.00,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,As you said, it doesn't work like in the movies.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.22,0:19:43.01,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,The reality doesn't work like you want it to.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.52,0:19:44.52,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.77,0:19:46.96,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.79,0:19:49.48,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to end it like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.74,0:19:50.62,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.91,0:19:52.73,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go to the old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.12,0:19:54.86,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,But he may not be at the hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.52,0:19:58.04,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you remember? He said he's going to Osaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.70,0:20:00.33,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,We can get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.19,0:20:18.87,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like we're on a bullet train.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.62,0:20:37.81,Default,man,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me... Is that scarf...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.52,0:20:54.69,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Old lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.21,0:20:56.79,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Old lady! Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.04,0:21:01.95,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,We got his name and address in the scarf!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.39,0:21:06.22,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,We told him your address!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.27,0:21:19.39,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,There she goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.78,0:21:20.28,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.20,0:21:22.94,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Will they get in touch?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.55,0:21:25.84,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Well... We'll see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.47,0:21:27.76,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,What would you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.34,0:21:32.60,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,If it were me, I wouldn't dismiss it as a fairy tale.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.25,0:21:35.71,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Not me and Kurashige-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.64,0:21:52.34,Default,preview,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage, senpai's coming back from London.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.32,0:21:53.04,Default,preview,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.04,0:21:55.79,Default,preview,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, Mikage. Promise you won't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.79,0:21:57.04,Default,preview,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.65,0:21:59.13,Default,preview,0000,0000,0000,,Next on Miracle Girls,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.13,0:22:00.66,Default,preview,0000,0000,0000,,"The Secret Is Revealed?!"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.16,0:22:03.50,Default,preview,0000,0000,0000,,Catch our telepathy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.88,0:22:08.09,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever we do,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.22,0:22:11.39,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,there has to be both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.31,0:22:14.73,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we had a fight,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.98,0:22:17.94,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,There has to be both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.82,0:22:34.58,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,There are days when kindness is so close
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.83,0:22:37.87,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,, that you can't see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.17,0:22:51.39,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we know it better than anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.93,0:22:57.81,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,When we can't say "I'm sorry,"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.89,0:23:04.86,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,we send out feelings through the little fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.61,0:23:11.62,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,Going over the tears,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.95,0:23:14.54,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,we want to be honest to ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.83,0:23:20.00,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause the sky deserves a rainbow.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.71,0:23:23.00,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever we do,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.21,0:23:26.51,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,there has to be both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.34,0:23:29.59,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,Two of us
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.72,0:23:32.93,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,are better than one of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.94,0:22:24.44,credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Ending Song\N"There has to be Both of Us"\N("Futarijanakya Dame Nano")\NBy Dio
